reviewText: Great show very talented group of young men
Very happy with product, would buy from this seller again!
We had it on DVR and it got deleted after a year  So glad I was able to purchase it
The DVD is awesome!  A must for any A7X fan.

Avenged Sevenfold is a great band. Synyster Gates who is the lead guitar player is one of the best guitar players in his generation. This concert movie is very great! They play flawlessly. This is one of the last concerts that their late drummer Jimmy "The rev" Sullivan who passed away in december of 2009.  I would recommend this concert video to anyone who likes the band Avenged Sevenfold.
Killer band. The DVD was so good. Me and my Gf Tammy got to see the band in Boston in 2014.
only official live concert with the rev, totally worth it. Avenged sevenfold all the way, RIP the rev.... buy this product
